column5: I wear my jock when I pick up my Yammy 4 stroke after winterizing, for sure.  $250.  Makes up for all the gas I save
ouch! considering I can run 2 full days on $30 in gas on my 4 stroke I'm not really sure what they're talking about...my former 2 stroke went through more than double
...then again, I did feel abused financially when I took it in for a tune-up. Cheap on gas, pricey in the shop
